name: Zool 2 [JAG]
description:
Zool 2 is an arcade game developed by Gremlin Interactive, Gremlin Graphics and Warp Factory. It came out on 01-01-1993. Gremlin Interactive published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Meh".
Zool 2 is available on Jaguar, Commodore / Amiga and PC.
It was scored by Neil Biggin and Patrick Phelan.
